      • getResponseCaPubsCA

        public String getResponseCaPubsCA​(String alias)
        Gets the semicolon separated list of CA IDs, to add the CA certificates to CMP response 'caPubs' field.
        Parameters:
        alias - the CMP configuration alias.
        Returns:
        the semicolon separated list of CA IDs.

      • setResponseCaPubsCA

        public void setResponseCaPubsCA​(String alias,
                                String caIdString)
        Sets the semicolon separated list of CA IDs, to add the CA certificates to CMP response 'caPubs' field. There are no checks performed, if the CAs for that IDs exist.
        Parameters:
        alias - the CMP configuration alias.
        caIdString - the semicolon separated list of CA IDs.
